lead_paragraph: Samu Kerevi's hopes of breaking into the Wallabies squad for the June internationals against England have been thrown in doubt after he suffered a broken hand in the Queensland Reds' win over the Cheetahs on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Hand Injury Set to Delay Kerevi's Australia Bow
